quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,"Ninahaza izina ry’Imana yawe Rurema Allah, Nyenicubahiro-ntangere (uvuge uti: “Sub-haana Rabbiya l-A’laa”)."
  87,2,"Yararemye ibiremwa, maze Iraringaniza indemo yavyo n’ibihimba; kimwe cose aho kigenewe, kibereye;"
  87,3,"Iraheza Irategekanya ivya nkenerwa vyose ku biremwa, Iranigisha kimwe cose ukuntu kivyikorako;"
  87,4,"Iranagisha n’uburagiro (ubwatsi);"
  87,5,"Hanyuma Irabukavya, busa n’urwatsi rutoto ruja kwirabura."
  87,6,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Twebwe Allah, Tuzokwigisha Qor’ani, ntuzoyibagira namba;"
  87,7,"Kiretse ico Imana Allah Ishatse ko wibagira ku neza y’ibiremwa. Mu vy’ukuri, ni Yo Izi ibigaragara mu bikorwa no mu majambo n’ibinyegeje muri vyo."
  87,8,"Tuzokworohereza gukora ivyoroshe; nko kwihanganira ishikirizabutumwa no kworoherezwa amabwirizwa y’idini."
  87,9,"Kubera ivyo rero, ibutsa abantu bawe warungitsweko gutumbera inzira igororotse, na canecane kwibutsa uwitezwe ko yibuka, nya kwibuka kukamugirira akamaro;"
  87,10,"Hazokwibuka uwutinya ibihano vy'Imana Allah."
  87,11,"Uwaseserejwe n’ivyaha na we, azoheza yigire kure y’urwo rwibutso;"
  87,12,"Ari na we azokwinjira mu muriro udahera ukaze bihambaye;"
  87,13,"Hanyuma ntazopfa muri wo ngo awuruhuke, eka ntazonawugiriramwo ubuzima buhimbaye."
  87,14,"Mu vy’ukuri yaramaze gutsinda, umuntu yiyejeje amabi;"
  87,15,"Akaninahaza n’izina ry’Imana yiwe Rurema Allah, maze agasenga amasengesho-bwirizwa ku mwanya, arondera gushimwa na Yo."
  87,16,"Bantu! Ahubwo rero, mushira imbere kurusha ubuzima bw’ibihendamaso vyo kw’isi;"
  87,17,"Kandi ubuzima bw’inyuma yo gupfa, ari bwo bwiza gusumba, kandi bwamaho."
  87,18,"Mu vy’ukuri, ivyo vyose mwadondaguriwe muri iki gisomwa, biri no mu Bitabu vy’aho hambere ya Qor’ani;"
  87,19,"Mu Mizingo y’Intumwa z’Imana Ibrahimu na Musa (za nyakugira amahoro y’Imana Allah)."
